# ── Dropped-in compiled harnesses ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Each shape's harness/ folder is where a user drops their compiled bundle.
# Those artifacts are per-user and must not be committed — keep only the
# placeholder and the *.example secret templates.
*/harness/*
!*/harness/DROP_COMPILED_FILES_HERE.md
!*/harness/*.example

# ── Secrets — never commit real values; only the .example templates ───────────
# Provider keys / tokens / RPC URLs live in `.env` (or `.dev.vars` for the
# cf-worker shapes). Templates end in `.example` and ARE committed.
.env
.env.local
.dev.vars
*/harness/.env
*/harness/.dev.vars

# ── Dependencies & lockfiles (generated when a harness is run) ────────────────
node_modules/
.bun/
bun.lock
bun.lockb
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# ── OS / editor cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
